readin2_rename <- figure1data_forplot %>%
  mutate(codename = paste0(code,"_",PLATE,"_",Position)) %>%
  filter(cfuA!=0 | cfuL!=0) %>%
  filter(!is.na(cfuA), !is.na(cfuL)) %>%
  mutate(total = cfuA + cfuL) %>%
  mutate(filtercol = "Y") %>% 
  mutate(repexp = paste0(code,"_",PLATE,"_"),codename = paste0(codename,"_"))

cfu_stats_for_qiime <- readin2_rename %>% dplyr::select(cfuA, cfuL) %>% t()

Figure 3C

figure2bv1 <- figure2bdata %>%
  filter(type == "fly") %>%
  group_by(Geography,Treatment,Sex,exp,Bacteria,Replicate,Plate,bottlegroup) %>%
  dplyr::summarize(meanA = mean(cfuA), meanL = mean(cfuL)) %>%
  ungroup() %>% 
  mutate(newbottle = paste0(Geography,Treatment,Sex,exp,Bacteria,Replicate,Plate,bottlegroup)) %>%
  dplyr::rename(cfuA = meanA, cfuL = meanL) %>%
  mutate(type = "fly") %>%
  rbind(figure2bdata %>%
          filter(Side == "A") %>%
          group_by(Geography,Treatment,Sex,exp,Bacteria,Replicate,Plate,bottlegroup) %>%
          dplyr::summarize(newcfuA1 = mean(cfuA), newcfuL1 = mean(cfuL)) %>%
          ungroup() %>%
          inner_join(figure2bdata %>%
                       filter(Side == "L") %>%
                       group_by(bottlegroup) %>%
                       dplyr::summarize(newcfuL2 = mean(cfuL), newcfuA2 = mean(cfuA)) %>% 
                       ungroup(),
                     by = "bottlegroup"
                     ) %>%
          mutate(newbottle = paste0(Geography,Treatment,Sex,exp,Bacteria,Replicate,Plate,bottlegroup)) %>%
          mutate(newcfuA = newcfuA1 + newcfuA2, newcfuL = newcfuL1 + newcfuL2) %>% 
          dplyr::select(-newcfuA1, -newcfuA2, -newcfuL1, -newcfuL2) %>%
          mutate(newbottle2 = newbottle) %>%
          dplyr::select(-newbottle) %>%
          dplyr::rename(newbottle=newbottle2) %>%
          rbind(figure2bdata %>%
                  filter(Side == "NA" & type == "diet") %>%
                  group_by(Geography,Treatment,Sex,exp,Bacteria,Replicate,Plate,bottlegroup) %>%
                  dplyr::summarize(newcfuA = mean(cfuA), newcfuL = mean(cfuL)) %>%
                  ungroup() %>%
                  mutate(newbottle = paste0(Geography,Treatment,Sex,exp,Bacteria,Replicate,Plate,bottlegroup))
                ) %>%
          dplyr::rename(cfuA = newcfuA, cfuL = newcfuL) %>%

        ) %>%
  mutate(Geography = factor(Geography, levels = rev(c("E", "B", "D", "H", "L", "PA", "M", "V"))))

## experiment-wise means group B and C, kept separate
f3bc <- f3bb %>%
  filter(!is.na(Geography)) %>%
#  group_by(Geography, Humidity, vialnum, Sex,Plate,starved,exp,repexp,latitude) %>%
  group_by(Geography, Humidity, Sex,starved,bacteria,exp,latitude) %>%
  dplyr::summarize(counts = mean(cfu)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(ghs = paste0(Geography, Humidity, Sex,bacteria,exp,latitude))

f3bd <- f3bc %>%
  filter(starved == "Y") %>%
  dplyr::select(ghs, Ycounts = counts) %>%
  inner_join(f3bc %>%
               filter(starved == "N") %>%
               dplyr::select(ghs, Ncounts = counts,Geography,Humidity, Sex,bacteria,exp,latitude)
  ) %>%
  mutate(transientA = Ncounts-Ycounts)

f3be <- f3bd %>%
  filter(bacteria == "LAB") %>%
  mutate(ghsb = paste0(Geography, Humidity, Sex,exp,latitude)) %>%
  dplyr::select(ghsb,cfuL = transientA) %>%
  inner_join(f3bd %>%
               filter(bacteria=="AAB") %>%

figure4cdata_forplot = figure1data %>% filter(Humidity != "A") %>% droplevels()

f4cb <- figure4cdata_forplot %>%
  mutate(cfu = cfuA, bacteria = "AAB") %>%
  dplyr::select(-cfuA, -cfuL) %>%
  rbind(figure4cdata_forplot %>%
          mutate(cfu = cfuL, bacteria = "LAB") %>%
          dplyr::select(-cfuA, -cfuL)
        ) %>%
  mutate(Geography = factor(Geography, levels = rev(c("E", "B", "D", "H", "L", "PA", "M", "V")))) %>%
  mutate(ghs = paste0(Geography,Humidity,Sex))

## experiment-wise means group B and C, kept separate
f4cc <- f4cb %>%
  filter(!is.na(Geography)) %>%
#  group_by(Geography, Humidity, vialnum, Sex,Plate,starved,exp,repexp,latitude) %>%
  group_by(Geography, Humidity, Sex,starved,bacteria,exp,latitude) %>%
  dplyr::summarize(counts = mean(cfu)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(ghs = paste0(Geography, Humidity, Sex,bacteria,exp,latitude))

f4cd <- f4cc %>%
  filter(starved == "Y") %>%
  dplyr::select(ghs, Ycounts = counts) %>%
  inner_join(f4cc %>%
               filter(starved == "N") %>%
               dplyr::select(ghs, Ncounts = counts,Geography,Humidity, Sex,bacteria,exp,latitude)
  ) %>%
  mutate(transientA = Ncounts-Ycounts)

f4ce <- f4cd %>%
  filter(bacteria == "LAB") %>%
  mutate(ghsb = paste0(Geography, Humidity, Sex,exp,latitude)) %>%
  dplyr::select(ghsb,cfuL = transientA) %>%
  inner_join(f4cd %>%
               filter(bacteria=="AAB") %>%
               mutate(ghsb = paste0(Geography, Humidity, Sex,exp,latitude)) %>%
               dplyr::select(ghsb,cfuA = transientA,Geography, Humidity, Sex, bacteria,exp,latitude),
             by = "ghsb") %>%
  rowwise() %>%
  mutate(Lperc = cfuL/(cfuL+cfuA)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  filter(Lperc>0, cfuL>0, cfuA>0)

figure5data <- readr::read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/johnchaston/microbiota2024/main/DataS3.csv",show_col_types = F, na = "") %>% mutate(vial=vial)

figure5data$S <- survival::Surv(figure5data$variable, figure5data$event)
figure5data$ft <- with(figure5data, interaction(sex, treatment))
figure5data$tf <- with(figure5data, interaction(treatment, sex))

model_all <- pairwise_survdiff(S ~ ft, data = figure5data, p.adjust.method = "BH")
x <- figure5data$ft
levs <- levels(x)
y <- Surv(figure5data$event,rep(1,length(figure5data$variable))) 
lvl_order <- levels(x)[order(tapply(as.numeric(y)[1:length(x)], x, mean))]

comps <- as_tibble(model_all$p.value, rownames="row") %>% 
  tidyr::pivot_longer(-row, names_to="col", values_to="p") %>% 
  na.omit()

mycomps <- as.matrix(comps[,1:2])
signif <- comps$p < .05

clds <- multcomp:::insert_absorb(signif, decreasing=FALSE, comps=mycomps, lvl_order=lvl_order)

cld_df <- clds$Letters %>% data.frame() %>% dplyr::rename(pvals = ".") %>% mutate(fruit = rownames(.))

#jpeg(width = 5.7, height = 5, filename = "figure5 coding.jpg", units = "in", res = 300)

readin2_rename <- optimize1 %>%
  mutate(codename = paste0(code,"_",PLATE,"_",Position)) %>%
  filter(cfuA!=0 | cfuL!=0) %>%
  filter(!is.na(cfuA), !is.na(cfuL)) %>%
  mutate(total = cfuA + cfuL) %>%
  mutate(filtercol = "Y") %>% 
  mutate(repexp = paste0(code,"_",PLATE,"_"),codename = paste0(codename,"_")) %>%
  mutate(vialnum = gsub(pattern = "#",replacement = "", x = vialnum)) %>%
  mutate(codename = gsub(pattern = "#",replacement = "", x = codename))

cfu_stats_for_qiime <- readin2_rename %>% dplyr::select(cfuA, cfuL) %>% t()
